          "text": "呔！留下买路金银，放你过去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要俺的金银却也不难，通上你的名来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "提起咱的威名，吓破你的心胆！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我也犯不上那么胆小，说你的吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且听道：咱就是二年前大闹江州，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "后投梁山，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与宋江、戴宗结拜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黑旋风李逵就是咱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喳喳喳，哇呀呀！嘿！都有假的，连俺李逵也会出来假的啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！咱已道出姓名，还不将金银献上！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要我的金银却也不难，胜得俺手中板斧，金银与你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听你这话，敢要与我分个上下？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳，要论个高低。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "招家伙吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李逵、李鬼对斧起打，双收下。）"
        }
      ],
