    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "李逵",
        "李鬼"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李逵上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住，黑汉倒有几分厉害，待我用反板斧伤他！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李鬼追上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里走！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李逵打倒李鬼。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看斧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎哟，好汉饶命！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢谢好汉。\n栽这么个跟头！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我来问你，你到底叫什么名字？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我叫黑面熊李鬼。李逵是冒充，我是个假的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我早知道你是个假的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "惭愧！请问好汉尊姓大名？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "提起俺的名姓，也吓破你的心胆！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "您还我一个“蹦子”。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且听道！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱就是二年前大闹江州，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "后投梁山，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与宋江、戴宗结拜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真真的黑旋风李逵就是咱啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喳喳喳！哇呀呀！哎哟，原来是李二哥……"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱们哪儿论的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，我真是千不该，万不该，不该劫夺二哥来。我这儿给您赔不是！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起来。我来问你，为何假冒我名，在此掳抢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二哥有所不知，只因小弟生性鲁莽，爱吃酒，好耍钱……"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么着，你爱吃酒，好耍钱？跟哥哥我，犯一路的毛病。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎哟，二哥你也好耍？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我也好耍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱们哥儿俩真是“吃西瓜喝凉水”犯一样的病啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可不是吗，后来怎样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无有银钱，奉养老母。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李逵自语。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他也有一个娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "因而来在这松林掳抢，冒充二哥的名姓，没想到今天就遇着您了。我这才叫圣\n人门前卖《三字经》，先打我个没趣儿。我也没脸活着了，二哥您拿斧子把我\n杀了吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢来慢来，要杀方才就把你杀了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李鬼羞。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嘿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我来问你，既有这身本领，是条英雄好汉，何不投奔梁山？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有意投奔梁山，只是无有引荐之人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愚兄愿做引荐之人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二哥与我作个引荐，咱们就走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢来，等愚兄回家探母回来之时，再与你奔往梁山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么着，您家里也有老娘吗？见了老太太，替我捎个好儿去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那个自然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里相会？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这……三日后望江楼相会。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "记下了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来来来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李逵取衣斧。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我这里有散碎银两，拿回家去，奉养老母。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，慢来慢来，二哥的银钱，小弟不敢收。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莫非嫌轻？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此愧领了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我弟兄分别了吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼、李逵",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我今赠银莫嫌轻，拿回家中奉娘亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢二哥赠我银，从今以后学好人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只要你真心来孝母，你母我娘俱不分。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日松林得相会，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二哥，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是假的你是真。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "取笑了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李鬼 （同笑） 啊哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二哥请转。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我弟兄在哪里相会？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方才言过：三日之后，沂州西门外，望江楼相会，记下了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "记下了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵、李鬼",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李逵下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个侠义的英雄，将俺打倒，不伤性命，反赠俺银两，约定三日后望江楼相\n会，同奔梁山；思想起来。好不喜煞人也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "俺李鬼与李逵巧得相会，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一样长相一样黑。\n却笑俺心粗胆壮敢作又敢为。\n假李逵偏偏就遇见了真李逵。\n我二人黑夜之间，乱杀乱砍分不出来谁和谁。\n又要俺同奔梁山作一个英雄好汉替天行道救困与扶危！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李鬼",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "归家去对老娘细说一回。"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "李逵→李鬼",
          "turns": 30
